00:16:14,541 --> 00:16:17,416
- HEY, NENE, CAN YOU HELP ME
LOAD THE NEW SYSTEM DOWNSTAIRS?

261
00:16:17,500 --> 00:16:18,833
- IT'S MS. NENE TO YOU!

262
00:16:18,916 --> 00:16:20,583
- BUT YOU'RE NOT
<i>THAT</i> MUCH OLDER THAN ME.

263
00:16:20,666 --> 00:16:21,833
- I AM MENTALLY!

264
00:16:21,916 --> 00:16:24,208
