HIS HANDS DIRTY.

304
00:18:50,916 --> 00:18:53,500
- HEY, DON'T STAND THERE.
GET INSIDE, QUICKLY.

305
00:18:53,583 --> 00:18:57,500
- THAT WAS PROFESSOR MASON,
