306
00:18:57,583 --> 00:19:00,750
- FORGET ABOUT IT.
- DID YOU TELL HIM ABOUT SYLIA?

307
00:19:10,125 --> 00:19:11,750
- STUPID KID.

308
00:19:11,833 --> 00:19:14,875
