SO MUCH YOUNGER THAN ME.

309
00:19:14,958 --> 00:19:19,208
- UGH, WHAT'S WRONG WITH ME?
AM I NUTS?

310
00:19:19,291 --> 00:19:23,166
- I FINALLY FOUND OUT THAT
WHAT MASON'S BEEN LOOKING FOR

311
00:19:23,250 --> 00:19:25,625
IS AN OLD UNDERGROUND RESEARCH
FACILITY CALLED THE WIZ LAB.

312
00:19:25,708 --> 00:19:28,583
- WAIT A MINUTE, I THOUGHT
MY FATHER'S LAB WAS DESTROYED.

313
00:19:28,666 --> 00:19:30,041
- THAT'S WHAT I BELIEVED,

314
00:19:30,125 --> 00:19:32,416
