ROSENKREUTZ'S KNOWLEDGE,

321
00:19:44,166 --> 00:19:45,166
I MIGHT ADD.

322
00:19:45,250 --> 00:19:47,541
- NO, HE CAN'T BE
LOOKING FOR THAT,

323
00:19:47,625 --> 00:19:49,166
IT MUST HAVE
BEEN DESTROYED!

324
00:19:49,250 --> 00:19:52,250
- I'M AFRAID THAT'S ALL I KNOW
AT THE MOMENT, GOOD-BYE.

325
00:19:52,333 --> 00:19:54,250
- ( monitor turns off )

326
00:19:58,416 --> 00:20:00,333
- ( crying )

