329
00:20:16,750 --> 00:20:18,250
- ABSOLUTELY PERFECT.

330
00:20:18,333 --> 00:20:20,750
I'M VERY FORTUNATE TO HAVE
EMPLOYEES LIKE YOU.

331
00:20:20,833 --> 00:20:23,000
